AIM

Our website aim is to provide easy house renting facility because of no broker involvement.

Tenants can be free from any stress of being scam or giving more money without much resource.

Ultimately, the goal is to facilitate the transaction process and help the property find its new owner.

TOOLS AND TECHNOLOGY:

HTML -  Hyper Text Markup Language is used to create basic structure of website

CSS - CSS is used to design website. Making it visualy attractive and easy to navigate. 

FUNCTIONALITY OF OUR WEBSITE:

1

Offer Service 

Our website provides new tenants 

services to shift their house if they 

new to city. So they can be stress free,

2

Inspection

It will update you with new rental houses in the searched area to customers.

3

Closing and Paperwork

Understand the closing process and paperwork to ensure a smooth and successful transaction.

Renting Your Home: 

Rental Price

Price ranges will be provided.

Legal Work

Allowance of legal property paperwork will be posted.

No Broker

Huge advantage of this website is that there will be no broker involved. So direct interaction between owner and tenants.

Time Saver

All the details of website will be clearly posted online with images and contact numbers so no need to rely on someone.

Advantages:

  •  One of the fundamental issues with yhe conventional procedure is the dealers cut,which is frequently quite  huge. There are no dealers in the digital network who can earn commission .

  • The use of online rental mechanisms improves the transparency of the entire rental process.The website through which you provide your services allows both the owner and tenants to communicate with one another via messaging network.

  • It is credible and protected to validate an online rental contract digitally with an e-signature. Furthermore, landlords can open the rental pact and additional official papers on their phone or desktop.
